rows.label: qst201911_msg0001
rows.name:
Where did you put our money?!
You must still be hiding it!

rows.label: qst201911_msg0002
rows.name: ...Wh-What are you talking about, mo?!

rows.label: qst201911_msg0003
rows.name: The money in the barrels!

rows.label: qst201911_msg0004
rows.name:
Didn't you split the money
you stole from us into four
barrels and bury them?!

rows.label: qst201911_msg0005
rows.name: We-We don't know, mo...

rows.label: qst201911_msg0006
rows.name: Enough with your lies!

rows.label: qst201911_msg0007
rows.name: You black-feathered fools...!

rows.label: qst201911_msg0008
rows.name: How long will you continue to mock us?!

rows.label: qst201911_msg0009
rows.name:
Now speak! If you do not speak
the truth, we will make sure
you never speak again!

rows.label: qst201911_msg0010
rows.name: Moooo!

rows.label: qst201911_msg0011
rows.name: Please forgive us, mo!

rows.label: qst201911_msg0012
rows.name:
Alala and friends
really don't know, mo!

rows.label: qst201911_msg0013
rows.name:
Only the leader knows about
the money in the barrels, mo!

rows.label: qst201911_msg0014
rows.name: The leader, you say?

rows.label: qst201911_msg0015
rows.name: Who is the leader?! Where is he?!

rows.label: qst201911_msg0016
rows.name:
Th-The leader is Suisui, mo!
The one you kicked away, mo!

rows.label: qst201911_msg0017
rows.name:
Suisui flew off somewhere
and is now missing, mo!

rows.label: qst201911_msg0019
rows.name:
Ah, well, yes. That
might have happened.

rows.label: qst201911_msg0020
rows.name:
Everyone, we are going to search
for Suisui. Prepare at once!

rows.label: qst201911_msg0021
rows.name:
No, searching on foot
would be a waste of time.

rows.label: qst201911_msg0022
rows.name: Then how shall we search?

rows.label: qst201911_msg0023
rows.name:
Let's have the members of the
mercenary group help us search.

rows.label: qst201911_msg0024
rows.name:
They should be able to find him much
faster than we could on our own.
